OL,3,CDrone show celebrates Year of Manx
OL,4,Clanguage in Douglas on Isle of Man
OL,6,FA drone show celebrating Blein ny
OL,7,FGaelgey - the Year of the Manx
OL,8,FLanguage - has been lighting up the
OL,9,Fskies in Douglas on the Isle of Man.
OL,11,FThe 15-minute display showcased a
OL,12,Fcombination of giant Manx words in the
OL,13,Fsky, created by a combination of
OL,14,Fprogrammed drones flying in formation.
OL,16,FThe event was organised by Douglas
OL,17,FCity Council, alongside Culture Vannin
OL,18,Fto mark the year of Manx Gaelic.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
