OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774210270
OL,3,CDrone show celebrates Year of Manx
OL,4,Clanguage in Douglas on Isle of Man
OL,6,FA number of Manx words appeared in the
OL,7,Fnight sky, alongside iconic imagery
OL,8,Ffrom the island including fairies and
OL,9,Fseals.
OL,11,FThe display was narrated to explain
OL,12,Fthe meaning of the Manx words, and the
OL,13,Fimportance of keeping the island
OL,14,Fculture alive.
OL,16,FThe Year of the Manx Language will see
OL,17,Fa number of events taking place across
OL,18,Fthe island to celebrate the culture
OL,19,Fand heritage of the Isle of Man.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
